    <div class="crowd-tip"><strong>Best time:</strong> Monday and Tuesday are the quietest days for cafés and shops, with short or no queues. The Sunday flea market at Birkelunden draws the largest weekend crowds from around 12:00 — arrive before 11:00 to browse before the main rush. Friday and Saturday evenings are the busiest for restaurants and bars on Thorvald Meyers gate. The Akerselva river path is walkable at any time and rarely crowded on weekday mornings.</div>
